The complete tamil contents of the website is present in fulldoc.txt. If you
make changes to this file or have a new file for the content, do the following:

python indexer.py <name_of_the_file>

This will create the indexes in the "index" directory (WARNING: Existing index
contents will be lost and the new index will be overwritten)

Update/upload this index folder to tamil thedal's main website
